title: Divinity.Original.Sin.2-CODEX
description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Divinity: Original Sin 2 (c) Larian Studios

Release Date : 09/2017 Protection : Steam
Discs : 1 Genre : Adventure

The Divine is dead. The Void approaches. And the powers latent
within you are soon to awaken. The battle for Divinity has begun.
Choose wisely and trust sparingly; darkness lurks within every
heart. Who will you be? A flesh-eating elf; an imperial lizard; an
undead risen from the grave? Choose your race and origin story - or
create your own! Discover how the world reacts differently to who -
and what - you are
